                "measurements at deuteron energies below 5.5 MeV were",
                "taken with 1.55 mg/cm2 thick evaporated foil;",
                "for the measurement of the angular distributions and",
                "the yield curve at higher energies a 2.84 mg/cm2 thick",
                "rolled foil was employed."
              ]
            }
          ],
